Package: bloodstream
Type: Package
Title: PET BIDS Blood Processing Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Granville J. Matheson
Maintainer: Granville J. Matheson <mathesong@gmail.com>
Description: bloodstream is a blood processing pipeline which 
    automatically processes PET BIDS blood data and produces derivative
    files ready for pharmacokinetic modelling. It allows users to decide
    which models it should apply, and it processes the data accordingly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
